('IFZA', '4773315', 'Biodegradable & Compostable Products Trading', 'Includes trading different kinds of products made out of resin, starch and natural substances that are designed to disintegrate and biodegrade in weeks, unlike the plastic products, it involves cutlery product, such as, knives, spoons, forks, plates, glasses, trays and other, also food and fruits wrappers, cling films and shopping bags, since these products dissolve in water and soil, then landfills are minimized, pollution reduced and positive impact in environment is produced.', 'Commercial', '', '', '', 'Non-Regulated', '', ''),
