('IFZA', '4773510', 'Electrical & Electronic Appliances Spare Parts Trading.', 'Includes reselling the spare parts of the audio-visual electronic equipment, involving radio sets, gramophones, loud-speakers television and video sets, , cinematography and television cameras, also, refrigerators, freezers, water coolers, washing machines and dryers, dishwashers, vacuum cleaners, ironers, heaters, electric kitchen mixers, mincers, cutters, blenders, toasters, juice extractors, grinders, kettles.', 'Commercial', '', '', '', 'Non-Regulated', '', ''),
