('IFZA', '4773713', 'Unmanned Aerial Vehicles (Drone) Trading', 'Includes reselling unmanned aerial vehicles (UAV) and Drones controlled by the remote control of a pilot on the ground, in order to use for survey, still and video imaging, mapping and inspection.', 'Commercial', '', 'Using this activity in restricted areas requires additional approval from the Ministry of Defense/Not allowed for freezone companies', 'Before license issuance', 'Regulated', 'Dubai Civil Aviation Authority', 'Security Industry Regulatory Agency - SIRA'),
